		+----+
		|MyIP|
		+----+
		
A Windows Phone app that provides the IP address of the phone. There is also a share via email feature.

Available for free at Windows Phone Marketplace: http://www.windowsphone.com/en-US/apps/00218e00-896e-e011-81d2-78e7d1fa76f8

The myip.php file that is downloaded from the App is the following:

<?php
 
function VisitorIP()
{ 
  if(isset($_SERVER['HTTP_X_FORWARDED_FOR']))
    $TheIp=$_SERVER['HTTP_X_FORWARDED_FOR'];
  else $TheIp=$_SERVER['REMOTE_ADDR'];
 
  return trim($TheIp);
}

echo VisitorIP();

?>

		+-----------------+
		|PasswordGenerator|
		+-----------------+

An app for Windows Phones that generates strong passwords. The user can them email the generated password.

Available for free at the Windows Phone Marketplace: http://www.windowsphone.com/en-US/apps/b42772db-70aa-e011-a53c-78e7d1fa76f8

		+------------+
		|Cryptography|
		+------------+
		
A Windows Phone App that provides simple encryption and decryption, by using an algorithm variant to Caesar's Encryption. 

Available for free at Windows Phone Marketplace: http://www.windowsphone.com/en-US/apps/f37056b7-81aa-e011-a53c-78e7d1fa76f8

		+-----------------+
		|PasswordGenerator|
		+-----------------+
		
A (very) simple Windows Phone app that provides a Lorem Ipsum-like text that can be copied or emailed.
Suitable for begginers in Windows Phone Development ;)

The app is available for free at Windows Phone Marketplace: http://www.windowsphone.com/en-US/apps/d14a5fa4-40aa-e011-a53c-78e7d1fa76f8


